Ti7 5 goeh8 15 ho7 Hoe2-chhia-lou7 u7 khui Thau3 kau3 Hou5-lou5-tun-ke. Tui3 hia kau3 Pek-kong-kheN tioh8 koe3 Tai7-kah kap Tai7-an nng7 tiau5 khe. Hit cham7 tai7-iok u7 nng7 phou3 goa7 lou7 e5 hng7; hit cham7 na7 cho7 chheng-chho2 chiu7 tui3 TaN2-kau2 kau3 Ke-lang5-thau5 long2 u7 thih-chhia-lou7. Hit cham7 cho7 iau2-boe7 ho2, ku2 u7 cho7 nng7 tiau5 e5 Kheng-pian7 chhia-lou7 chin ho2-eng7.   
Hian7-si5 tui3 Tai5-lam5 pak e5 cha2-chhia Si7 6 tiam2 cheng hoat, hit me5 9 tiam2 cheng chiu7 kau3 Tai5-pak; an2-ni Tai5-lam5 kau3 Tai5-pak chit8 jit8 chiu7 kau3 ui7.   
